node.title: ManawatÅ« River searched after 11yo and woman fail to surface
node.description: An air, water and ground search is ongoing.
node.content:
["A search is underway on the Manawatū River after two people failed to surface after going underwater.", "Emergency services were notified of the incident near Maxwell's Line at 3:15pm, near to a popular swimming spot.
", "Police have confirmed that an 11-year-old girl got into difficulty in the river. A 25-year-old woman went in after her and both disappeared.
", "Family at the scene weren't able to locate them and called emergency services.
", "An air, water and ground search is ongoing, with reports that multiple helicopters are on the scene.
", "The river has been swollen from heavy rain and the resulting discolouration of the water is likely to complicate the search.
"]
